TopicTitle: 1.0 Crashes when I try to go to the VAB

Articles.Content:
So I installed the new version. Had a few mods, made a fresh save, accepted two contracts and went to the VAB. In the loading screen the game just crashes.

Tried twice more and the same.

Deleted the mods and the same happened

Fresh install of the game and same thing happened.

Did a fresh save after the fresh install and still no cigar... =(

It seems like I'm the only one having this issue as no one else seems to have reported this bug. Why is it?
remove -force-opengl of the launch options, work for me.

launch options? what? where is that?

thank you
